  "title": "이수한의원에서 2016년에도 따뜻한 크리스마스",
  "addDate": "2016. 12. 21.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220891404369",
  "html_size": 196040,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220891404369\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220891404369\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">안녕하세요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">요즘 날씨가 추웠다가 시원했다가 더웠다가 하네요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이럴때 모두 감기 조심하셔야 해요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">다들 잘 아시죠?&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">코랑 목은 항상 따뜻하게 목도리나 마스크로 잘 가리구</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">장갑도 꼭 끼구 다니시구요 ^^&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">음...</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">크리스마스가 몇일 안남았어요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">2016년 1월 1일이 몇일전인거만 같은데</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">벌써 12월이 다 끝나가고있어요&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">날이 갈수록 시간이 너무 빨리 가는거 같아요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">ㅠㅠㅠㅠ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">저만 느끼나요?&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e99805d963476e94.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-12\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">오늘은 우리 환자분께서 선물을 주셨어요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">큰 하얀 박스 하나랑 작은 노랑 박스 두개</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">작은 박스 두개는 뭔지 아시는 분은 아실거에요 그쵸? ^^</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNjEyMjFfMTg4/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTAzNjI0.fPheXXd1z1SAoJj0v7oQxs0D9Wlcr8e2EF-OhZlpjLQg.dwloUg5wFVtKp4UrSswEiGjDLdQX_Z-6hA6nx4AemDgg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122630031.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjFfMTg4/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTAzNjI0.fPheXXd1z1SAoJj0v7oQxs0D9Wlcr8e2EF-OhZlpjLQg.dwloUg5wFVtKp4UrSswEiGjDLdQX_Z-6hA6nx4AemDgg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122630031.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E275851')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNjEyMjFfMTg4/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTAzNjI0.fPheXXd1z1SAoJj0v7oQxs0D9Wlcr8e2EF-OhZlpjLQg.dwloUg5wFVtKp4UrSswEiGjDLdQX_Z-6hA6nx4AemDgg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122630031.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">사랑의 에그타르트</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/997122c179ce86d7.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-8\"></a>&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0a1605162cf3eaf8.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjFfMTcg/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTAzODU4.mTOgw4foysMLuFlzYEc9UPGfepxPkmAv3xe-M6ArvsEg.DFqruQQBY_1LEcNXzJGylKfUUcvV4GueqWqx5gFFFbgg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122630429.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E275851')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0a1605162cf3eaf8.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">자 이제 큰박스를 한번 열어볼까요?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">두둥</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNjEyMjFfMTE4/MDAxNDgyMzAwNjI5NTUx.or9X4nFhuexrpU7zqbxOiBUDbHrMZvxfTvAtxXqQYqMg.jQUlJOfYV2Qt-oGL8Cnmgk9LEE_IwEeGWj3EPq1pR3Ig.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122630714.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjFfMTE4/MDAxNDgyMzAwNjI5NTUx.or9X4nFhuexrpU7zqbxOiBUDbHrMZvxfTvAtxXqQYqMg.jQUlJOfYV2Qt-oGL8Cnmgk9LEE_IwEeGWj3EPq1pR3Ig.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122630714.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E275851')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNjEyMjFfMTE4/MDAxNDgyMzAwNjI5NTUx.or9X4nFhuexrpU7zqbxOiBUDbHrMZvxfTvAtxXqQYqMg.jQUlJOfYV2Qt-oGL8Cnmgk9LEE_IwEeGWj3EPq1pR3Ig.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122630714.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">바로 보이면 좀 싱거우니까</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">살짝 가려주는 센스</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/64e9b72df78c6cf4.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-35\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNjEyMjFfMjcz/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTA0MTg1.xFHYmW1zeiLx_RnMosedwiR-ob4Xtgq5NmfC0FaJ6OUg.f69ETgzjA4JJr7xdNuyUhrKiyIlFCeFf4OnoS8G-eMcg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122631152.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjFfMjcz/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTA0MTg1.xFHYmW1zeiLx_RnMosedwiR-ob4Xtgq5NmfC0FaJ6OUg.f69ETgzjA4JJr7xdNuyUhrKiyIlFCeFf4OnoS8G-eMcg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122631152.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E275851')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNjEyMjFfMjcz/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTA0MTg1.xFHYmW1zeiLx_RnMosedwiR-ob4Xtgq5NmfC0FaJ6OUg.f69ETgzjA4JJr7xdNuyUhrKiyIlFCeFf4OnoS8G-eMcg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122631152.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">이제 열어볼께요</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">짜잔</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">올~</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c2afe4fc68ab836b.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjFfMjYw/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTA1Mzc3.-1t5S9ijzkkhYvYacu-qMDuaPe-xwKTw1kY6n3koxj8g.tWre9Mwh3Y6viaGNQuWpbtPxCeCSrcVsVrcCoh5QHDkg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122631618.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E275851')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c2afe4fc68ab836b.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">글러브랑.. 가방이네요</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">디자인도 심플해서 이쁘고&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">색도 검정이라 너무 이쁘네요</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">우리 환자분 역시 보는 눈이 높으셔요&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/be15837a2d144691.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-20\"></a>&nbsp;</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3c58ee2c135561b2.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjFfMyAg/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTA1Njc1.DARNAGieJUK9fQY7d5Ig0MuyZXrlGvJMTEYX7ZCHSDMg.qlCLOg8u3hKzp-avPK_W0nxksQP7MK1BNNaccYbwmngg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122631962.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E275851')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3c58ee2c135561b2.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8b4e83222ff72d3f.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjFfMTM2/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTA1OTQ2.yw8rINgTAlSe5b11RYObC8p4FlS5C0gtSzZUYabVTfcg.j-3XVsAL20nK8PyAUNmH2wmthtZvMzwzccqlEvFMsoQg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122632267.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E275851')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8b4e83222ff72d3f.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">(좀 탐나네요 &nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">원장님 선물이라 뺏지도 못하고&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">뺏으면 나쁜직원 되니까 그냥 눈으로만 봅니다 ㅎㅎㅎ)</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">아 근대 진짜 심플해서 이쁘고</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">제질도 좋아서 너무 좋아보여요</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/30230dc6071cf57d.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjFfMTc5/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTA2Mjkx.eAots-SB9sHt1d8ZcesfvITvdoV1oqI0yib0TWAHtrgg.4reEm1xIX1Ec8MXBgbrwFMv69FIzkE0mRbJvzfyTyF8g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122632696.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E275851')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/30230dc6071cf57d.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f212061a369c3679.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjFfNzUg/MDAxNDgyMzAwNTA2NTI3.Va-6pZFoUdSlX-Dv4ceyuExAx-dN0p5jkQDZlZJl59Ig.-Boz8Sr0Xp7v-dzkrYFv4vQW5XGjU1P-11JQgcuNe7gg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161221_122633029.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E275851')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f212061a369c3679.jpg\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">우리 원장님 좋으시겠어요~</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">날씨는 추워도</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">우리 이수한의원은 항상 이렇게 좋으신분들 덕뿐에</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">언제나 따뜻하답니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">선물주신 우리 착하고 이쁜 환자분,</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">감사합니다 ^^ 타르트도 잘먹겠습니다 ^^</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">몇일남지 않은 2016년 크리스마스</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">모두 잘 행복하고 즐겁게 보내시구</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">미리 메리 크리스마스요 ㅎㅎ</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_choco\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7c5f1453eeae2295.png\" alt=\"line_choco-11\"></a>&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
